### Register
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"test2@example.com","password":"Password123!"}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"test2@example.com","password":"Password123!"}

